source: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_SEQ_00<tab>Keitha, the head wrangler at Bentbranch Meadows, wishes you to gather roselet seeds from which she hopes to extract an oil known to calm agitated chocobos.
target: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_SEQ_00<tab>Keitha, the head wrangler at Bentbranch Meadows, wishes you to gather roselet seeds from which she hopes to extract an oil known to calm agitated chocobos.

source: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_SEQ_02<tab>You have collected six roselet seeds. Deliver them to Keitha at Bentbranch Meadows.
target: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_SEQ_02<tab>You have collected six roselet seeds. Deliver them to Keitha at Bentbranch Meadows.

source: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_SEQ_03<tab>Having delivered the roselet seeds to Keitha, the head wrangler admits she is none the wiser as to what might have been troubling her chocobos. She remains hopeful, nevertheless, that the oil obtained from the seeds will help to calm the distressed birds.
target: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_SEQ_03<tab>Having delivered the roselet seeds to Keitha, the head wrangler admits she is none the wiser as to what might have been troubling her chocobos. She remains hopeful, nevertheless, that the oil obtained from the seeds will help to calm the distressed birds.

source: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_KEITHA_000_1<tab>Seein' as you're here, I've got a favor to ask: gather me six seeds from those plantlike monsters they call roselets.
target: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_KEITHA_000_1<tab>Seein' as you're here, I've got a favor to ask: gather me six seeds from those plantlike monsters they call roselets.

source: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_KEITHA_000_2<tab>The oil from them roselet seeds has a calmin' effect on skittish chocobos, see. Any wrangler worth her salt usually has a jar or two lyin' around.
target: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_KEITHA_000_2<tab>The oil from them roselet seeds has a calmin' effect on skittish chocobos, see. Any wrangler worth her salt usually has a jar or two lyin' around.

source: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_KEITHA_000_3<tab>I thought the stock I had would last me a good while, but lately the birds've been as restless as a summer storm.
target: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_KEITHA_000_3<tab>I thought the stock I had would last me a good while, but lately the birds've been as restless as a summer storm.

source: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_KEITHA_000_4<tab>Chocobos are sensitive creatures at the best o' times, and it ain't unusual for 'em to act a shade agitated all of a sudden... But this is somethin' else.
target: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_KEITHA_000_4<tab>Chocobos are sensitive creatures at the best o' times, and it ain't unusual for 'em to act a shade agitated all of a sudden... But this is somethin' else.

source: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_KEITHA_000_5<tab>You'll find them roselets I mentioned up near Galvanth's Spire. Go on now, time's a-wastin'.
target: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_KEITHA_000_5<tab>You'll find them roselets I mentioned up near Galvanth's Spire. Go on now, time's a-wastin'.

source: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_KEITHA_000_10<tab>Did you have any trouble gettin' them seeds?
target: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_KEITHA_000_10<tab>Did you have any trouble gettin' them seeds?

source: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_KEITHA_000_11<tab>Let's see here...one, two, three...yep, there's the full six. Nice big ones, too. We'll squeeze some good oil out o' these.
target: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_KEITHA_000_11<tab>Let's see here...one, two, three...yep, there's the full six. Nice big ones, too. We'll squeeze some good oil out o' these.

source: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_KEITHA_000_12<tab>I still don't have a clue what's been unsettlin' the birds, but whatever it is, hopefully the roselet oil will help calm 'em down a bit...
target: TEXT_SUBFST050_00156_KEITHA_000_12<tab>I still don't have a clue what's been unsettlin' the birds, but whatever it is, hopefully the roselet oil will help calm 'em down a bit...
